82
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:10,520
- No.
- That's right, then.

83
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:14,820
You and Xiao'en are both very important to me.

84
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:17,520
Aoran, don't overthink it.

85
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:20,080
Just focus on being happy.

86
00:07:57,690 --> 00:07:59,960
So handsome!

87
