92
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:08,420
To be liked.

93
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:42,310
Zheng Xiao'en, promise me something.

94
00:10:42,310 --> 00:10:44,350
As long as I reach out my hand,

95
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:46,390
I will be able to touch you.

96
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:49,060
This is the farthest distance you can be away from me.

97
00:10:58,610 --> 00:11:02,810
You're the one I like, Situ Aoran.

98
00:11:02,810 --> 00:11:05,080
You're one of a kind.

99
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,050
Nobody can replace you.

100
00:11:09,050 --> 00:11:11,240
No matter who you are,

101
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:16,600
you're one of a kind in my heart.

102
00:11:17,990 --> 00:11:21,010
No one will ever be able to replace you.

103
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:28,470
It's so wonderful to have you in this world.

104
00:11:31,570 --> 00:11:33,260
I love you.

105
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:36,570
I will love you forever.

106
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,430
Meeting you

107
00:12:09,930 --> 00:12:13,930
