108
00:12:56,670 --> 00:12:59,070
Xiao'en, where are you—

109
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:33,320
No. This can’t be.

110
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,190
I haven't said "I love you" yet.

111
00:13:35,190 --> 00:13:37,270
We haven't exchanged rings yet.

112
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,910
All this still hasn’t ended.

113
00:13:38,910 --> 00:13:41,930
This doesn't count! It can't!

114
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:57,350
With everyone’s blessings, they finally lived happily ever after.

115
00:14:22,210 --> 00:14:26,370
Xiao... Xiao'en?

116
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:34,620
Doctor! Doctor!

117
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,710
This place is...?

118
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:42,690
You're finally awake.

119
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:47,040
You don’t know how frantic I’ve been, seeing you like this!

120
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,490
You scared me to death!

121
00:14:48,490 --> 00:14:52,410
Qiutian, speak slower.

122
00:14:52,410 --> 00:14:56,110
What Qiutian? I'm Chuntian.

123
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:57,800
Chuntian?

124
00:14:57,800 --> 00:15:00,410
Yes, Chuntian.

125
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,770
You don’t recognize me anymore?

126
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:09,080
When did you turn back into Chuntian?

127
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,710
What are you saying?

128
00:15:10,710 --> 00:15:14,160
Zheng Xiao'en, don't scare me.

129
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:16,110
When will the doctor get here?

130
00:15:16,110 --> 00:15:17,940
Doctor!

131
00:15:18,810 --> 00:15:22,910
You're really Chuntian?

132
00:15:24,070 --> 00:15:26,990
So I'm back?

133
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:30,920
I didn't disappear.

134
00:15:33,250 --> 00:15:35,540
Then what about Aoran?

135
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:37,800
What about Aoran? What happened to Aoran?

136
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:39,890
What do you mean disappeared?

137
00:15:39,890 --> 00:15:41,950
Zheng Xiao'en, don't move.

138
00:15:41,950 --> 00:15:43,940
I'll go get the doctor.

139
00:15:57,940 --> 00:16:00,380
What’s going on? Call someone! Hurry up and call someone!

140
00:16:00,380 --> 00:16:02,280
Hurry!

141
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:10,470
Please leave the room for a while first.

142
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:19,710
Zheng Xiao'en, what are you doing?

143
00:16:19,710 --> 00:16:20,980
I have to find Situ Aoran.

144
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:23,560
Situ Aoran? Isn't that a character in a novel?

145
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:25,950
Do you have to be that dedicated to your work?

146
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:30,230
He Tianxing. I have to find He Tianxing.

147
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:31,830
I'm awake, so he must be awake too.

148
00:16:31,830 --> 00:16:33,400
What are you saying?

149
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,830
And with your physical condition like this, why are you looking for He Tianxing?

150
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:37,880
Just take it as a plea from me. Don’t move around, okay? Zheng Xiao’en!

151
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:42,200
Nurse, quickly help to examine her. Are there sequelae because she was lying down for three months?

152
00:16:43,050 --> 00:16:44,600
I’ve been lying down for three months?

153
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:48,460
That’s right. So now you have to recuperate properly first.

154
00:16:51,750 --> 00:16:53,740
I'll go get the doctor.

155
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:59,360
You’ll really anger me to death.

156
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:02,090
Why don’t you help me to call He Tianxing?

157
00:17:02,090 --> 00:17:05,190
Is He Tianxing your puppy? You just call him and he’ll come?

158
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:08,350
He recognizes me. If you go and find him, he’ll definitely come!

159
00:17:08,350 --> 00:17:10,010
Only a ghost will come.

160
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:12,300
The hospital he was at before had a fire.

161
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:14,530
After that, there's been no news of He Tianxing.

162
00:17:14,530 --> 00:17:16,960
Maybe he’s dead.

163
00:17:18,530 --> 00:17:20,150
It’s not possible. He can’t possibly be dead.

164
00:17:20,150 --> 00:17:21,900
Please let me find him!

165
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:23,900
Zheng Xiao'en!

166
00:17:23,900 --> 00:17:25,070
Hey!

167
00:17:25,070 --> 00:17:27,850
Xiao'en! Sit down first.

168
00:17:27,850 --> 00:17:30,060
Don’t move around. Lie down first.

169
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:34,060
Lie down first.

170
00:17:36,620 --> 00:17:40,410
Doctor! Doctor!

171
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,600
Who are you guys?

172
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:49,770
Get out of the way!

173
00:17:49,770 --> 00:17:51,490
Let go of me!

174
00:17:51,490 --> 00:17:53,990
Who are you guys?

175
00:17:56,630 --> 00:17:58,820
- Don’t move!
- Come here.

176
00:17:59,670 --> 00:18:01,400
The patient is in a very critical condition right now.

177
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,150
If we don’t do anything, the patient will die.

178
00:18:03,150 --> 00:18:04,440
I want him to die.

179
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:06,380
[Asystole]

180
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:08,560
Tianxing!

181
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,940
Where are you going?

182
00:18:26,890 --> 00:18:30,180
♫ My last wish is to never regret ♫

183
00:18:30,180 --> 00:18:36,290
♫ Brave out the heartbreak to no longer be afraid of heartbreaks ♫

184
00:18:36,290 --> 00:18:42,900
♫ I choose to bid farewell with a smile ♫

