00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:54,420
[Asystole]

190
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:56,630
Tianxing!

191
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,930
Where are you going?

192
00:19:13,190 --> 00:19:15,520
Hold on!

193
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:17,640
Move aside!

194
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:23,540
Stop staring blankly! Help him quickly!

195
00:19:53,970 --> 00:19:55,930
Let go.

196
00:19:58,100 --> 00:19:59,570
Are you all right?

197
00:19:59,570 --> 00:20:02,690
I’m all right. I’ll go and have a look at Tianxing first.

198
00:20:09,570 --> 00:20:11,590
- Why did you come?
- I came to save someone.

199
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:13,660
Save someone?

200
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:15,860
Are you sure you saved the right person?

201
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:18,780
You probably won't believe me when I say this,

202
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:22,440
but Miss can only be saved if He Tianxing lives.

203
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:30,750
A whole group of people couldn't take care of one patient?

204
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:33,200
I want results not excuses!

205
00:20:34,670 --> 00:20:38,130
Since you accepted my money, you must properly take care of things.

206
00:20:38,130 --> 00:20:39,850
I'll say it again.

207
00:20:39,850 --> 00:20:43,130
The results I want are those that will make me satisfied.

208
00:20:43,130 --> 00:20:45,000
Do you understand?

209
00:20:49,130 --> 00:20:53,080
Tianliang is the kingdom I created.

210
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:55,630
No one can get in my way.

211
00:20:57,090 --> 00:21:00,910
I've been waiting too long. Too long.

212
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:05,860
Tianxing.

213
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:07,700
Tianxing.

214
00:21:09,860 --> 00:21:12,860
I almost thought you wouldn't be able to hang in there anymore.

215
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:17,520
Thank goodness we didn't give up earlier when your heart suddenly stopped.

216
00:21:21,390 --> 00:21:24,290
This time, you really slept for too long.

217
00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:26,320
I knew you wouldn't give up.

218
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:28,710
I knew you wouldn't make me wait for no reason.

219
00:21:28,710 --> 00:21:31,940
This is the He Tianxing I know.

220
00:21:37,610 --> 00:21:40,110
Progress on the medical biotechnology project we invested in needs to speed up

221
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:42,280
Separately, find a couple of people for me.

222
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:46,560
Under the names of Tianliang Construction, Tianliang Transportation, Tianliang Digital, and Tianliang Textile,

223
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:50,030
invest aggressively into those four startup companies on the Cayman Islands.

224
00:21:50,030 --> 00:21:51,780
Do you understand?

225
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:54,990
Yes. Get it done promptly.

