234
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:06,710
From your left, my right.

235
00:23:08,670 --> 00:23:11,260
It looks like there are no problems.

236
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:19,940
Brain MRI, normal. EEG, normal. EKG, normal.

237
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:22,340
The neurology exam also came back normal.

238
00:23:22,340 --> 00:23:26,350
But before, she would occasionally start bleeding.

239
00:23:26,350 --> 00:23:28,260
Her blood tests also came back normal.

240
00:23:28,260 --> 00:23:31,790
There are no issues with her platelet count and coagulation functions.

241
00:23:31,790 --> 00:23:34,910
So Xiao'en's condition right now is...

242
00:23:34,910 --> 00:23:37,700
Simply put, her condition right now is that of a healthy baby.

243
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:40,390
Miss Zheng, congratulations, you can be discharged.

244
00:23:40,390 --> 00:23:42,290
Thank you.

245
00:23:44,390 --> 00:23:46,040
All normal?

246
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:48,790
Before, her head started bleeding while she was asleep.

247
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:50,960
Was that normal?

248
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:55,080
Or is there something else we forgot to check?

249
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,920
