250
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:01,130
I think we should stay in the hospital a couple more days—

251
00:24:01,130 --> 00:24:02,610
You're a professional nurse.

252
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:04,370
Have you heard of a patient named He Tianxing?

253
00:24:04,370 --> 00:24:06,050
He should be in a VVIP room.

254
00:24:06,050 --> 00:24:07,920
No, I haven't.

255
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:10,250
But you must know a lot of VVIPs.

256
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:12,530
- Please ask for me. His name's He Tianxing.
- Sorry, my friend just returned to Earth.

257
00:24:12,530 --> 00:24:14,730
She's still learning how to be a normal person.

258
00:24:14,730 --> 00:24:18,170
You... Aoran must be—

259
00:24:18,170 --> 00:24:20,670
It's Tianxing. Tianxing must be anxiously looking for me.

260
00:24:20,670 --> 00:24:21,990
He just doesn't know where to find me.

261
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:23,900
I must hurry and find him.

262
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:26,030
Tianxing is anxiously looking for you?

263
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:29,050
Are you serious?

264
00:24:29,590 --> 00:24:32,630
The doctor lied to me. You're not well at all.

265
00:24:32,630 --> 00:24:34,990
Doctor!

266
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:45,990
[Green Mountain Psychiatric Sanatorium]

267
00:24:57,820 --> 00:25:03,150
When you woke up that day, you suddenly shouted at someone asking where they were going.

268
00:25:04,690 --> 00:25:08,190
It was just a dream. Why do you keep asking about it?

269
00:25:08,190 --> 00:25:12,040
Because he sounded very anxious. I'm curious.

270
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:23,680
Tianxing, even though we narrowly escaped this time,

271
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:26,530
your brother will definitely make another attempt.

272
00:25:26,530 --> 00:25:30,000
It's because he knows that as long as the CEO is alive,

273
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:33,000
he won't be able to take over Tianliang Group.

274
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:36,420
On top of that, the sanatorium was exposed.

275
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:39,150
We must quickly find a place for you to settle down.

276
00:25:39,150 --> 00:25:42,260
Otherwise, you won't be able to sleep well.

277
00:25:44,220 --> 00:25:48,010
Let's think about a good place to hide.

278
00:25:58,150 --> 00:26:01,820
Or do you have other thoughts?

279
00:26:22,590 --> 00:26:26,590
Chuntian, thank you.

280
00:26:27,260 --> 00:26:31,110
It must've been hard taking care of me the past three months.

281
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:32,480
Don't mention it.

282
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:36,540
It's worth it seeing you awake now.

283
00:26:36,540 --> 00:26:38,890
If...

284
00:26:40,780 --> 00:26:49,130
I mean if... in the case that... suppose that...

285
00:26:49,890 --> 00:26:52,450
I kind of didn't want to wake up,

286
00:26:52,450 --> 00:26:54,600
would you be angry?

287
00:26:55,670 --> 00:27:00,210
I didn't know I was so narrow-minded in your eyes.

288
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:05,250
You understand me so well.

289
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:06,850
That's right! I would be angry.

290
00:27:06,850 --> 00:27:09,220
Once was enough. You're not allowed to do this again.

291
00:27:09,220 --> 00:27:11,600
You stay alive and well. You hear me?

292
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:14,940
Of course.

293
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:26,520
I'll clean it up. You go and get some rest.

294
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:29,990
No, I can do it.

295
00:27:58,330 --> 00:28:01,450
What are you doing? I said I would do it!

296
00:28:01,450 --> 00:28:03,350
Does it hurt a lot?

297
00:28:06,290 --> 00:28:08,520
It doesn't hurt at all.

298
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:12,990
Chuntian, am I still dreaming?

299
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:15,140
That must be it.

300
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:16,790
I'm still in the dream, right?

301
00:28:16,790 --> 00:28:19,020
That's why it doesn't hurt.

302
00:28:20,820 --> 00:28:24,660
When I wake up from this dream, I'll be able to see Aoran when I open my eyes.

303
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:28,160
Aoran? Are you close to him?

304
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:31,660
All you did was proofread drafts, and you call this seeing him?

305
00:28:32,380 --> 00:28:37,530
Or... is pressure from work really that bad?

306
00:28:37,530 --> 00:28:40,540
No, I really do know Aoran, and we also—

307
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:43,470
Okay, okay, the novel is already published.

308
00:28:43,470 --> 00:28:45,620
It's okay. Nothing to worry about.

309
00:28:45,620 --> 00:28:48,660
And I think you need to rest up.

310
00:28:48,660 --> 00:28:50,550
Go to sleep after I finish wrapping this.

311
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:52,920
See if you'll be more clear-headed after some rest.

312
00:28:56,690 --> 00:28:59,800
Okay. You should leave.

313
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:02,480
No, I'm going to stay here with you.

314
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:06,180
No need. I'm not a patient. I don't need you to stay with me.

315
00:29:06,180 --> 00:29:10,440
I do. I don't care. You need to stay with me.

316
00:29:25,100 --> 00:29:27,900
Tianjian, I don't feel at ease.

317
00:29:27,900 --> 00:29:29,540
I want to go see your sister.

318
00:29:29,540 --> 00:29:31,200
Please take me there.

319
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:33,890
Sis is fine. Just let her rest.

320
00:29:33,890 --> 00:29:35,880
But I haven't heard from her at all.

321
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,450
My heart is uneasy.

322
00:29:37,450 --> 00:29:39,960
And I don't how she's doing. Is she getting better?

323
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:42,580
Of course. We already arranged for the best doctors for her.

324
00:29:42,580 --> 00:29:43,800
Don't worry, okay?

325
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:46,240
Then, when can she come home?

326
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,770
She'll come back when she's better!

327
00:29:47,770 --> 00:29:50,000
I'm not a doctor, but you keep asking me!

328
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,330
How am I supposed to know?

329
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,840
Hello?

330
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:01,970
Mom, turn on the TV!

331
00:30:04,090 --> 00:30:06,400
The news channel!

332
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:08,520
After Tianliang Group's former CEO, He Tianxing,

333
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:11,450
fell from a building and was taken to a hospital, his whereabouts became a mystery.

334
00:30:11,450 --> 00:30:14,890
After three months of being hidden away, we finally have some news today.

335
00:30:14,890 --> 00:30:18,330
Let's take you onsite to the medical team's press conference.

336
00:30:18,330 --> 00:30:22,940
After multiple rescue efforts on our part, Mr. He has finally awakened and regained consciousness.

337
00:30:22,940 --> 00:30:25,050
Then, when did He Tianxing get transferred to the sanatorium?

338
00:30:25,050 --> 00:30:27,270
- When will you know the outcome?
- When will he be discharged?

339
00:30:27,270 --> 00:30:30,000
- Could you tell us?
- Can you provide a clearer explanation?

340
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:32,430
- What will the outcome be?
- When can he be discharged?

341
00:30:33,910 --> 00:30:36,100
A big thanks to the medical team for their rescue efforts.

342
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:39,950
Mr. He was able to regain consciousness not only due to Dr. Sun's help.

343
00:30:39,950 --> 00:30:43,210
We believe his strong will to live also played a critical role.

344
00:30:43,210 --> 00:30:46,470
He's awake. He's at Green Mountain Psychiatric Sanatorium.

345
00:30:46,470 --> 00:30:48,470
I saw it. So?

346
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:51,780
- I need to go see him.
- What for?

347
00:30:51,780 --> 00:30:53,390
He's waiting for me.

348
00:30:53,390 --> 00:30:55,480
He must be waiting for me.

349
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,630
What are we performing now?

350
00:30:58,630 --> 00:31:00,580
Who's going to give me a recap?

351
00:31:00,580 --> 00:31:02,640
Zheng Xiao'en, wait for me.

352
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:06,100
Who knew this trick would work?

353
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:09,980
Sure enough, the most dangerous place is the safest place.

354
00:31:10,630 --> 00:31:14,350
That's right. What the CEO said was right.

355
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:17,360
Instead of hiding, it's better to just expose everything.

356
00:31:17,360 --> 00:31:20,430
This way, reporters will keep their eyes on the CEO 24 hours a day.

357
00:31:20,430 --> 00:31:23,330
So if He Tianjian wants to do something to him, it would be difficult.

358
00:31:23,330 --> 00:31:27,300
No wonder the Young Master and Miss could never defeat him.

359
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:32,760
Miss, visiting hours have passed.

360
00:31:32,760 --> 00:31:34,610
Please, I want to see Tianxing.

361
00:31:34,610 --> 00:31:36,230
Mr. He has rejected visitors.

362
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:39,040
I'm not a visitor. He and I are—

363
00:31:39,790 --> 00:31:43,660
Our relationship is a bit hard to describe.

364
00:31:43,660 --> 00:31:46,970
Or you could pretend to not have seen me.

365
00:31:57,980 --> 00:32:00,150
Miss, you can't go in!

366
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:09,990
Don't run!

367
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:15,130
VIP... VIP.

368
00:32:15,130 --> 00:32:17,360
[VIP rooms]

369
00:32:19,470 --> 00:32:20,980
She's right there! Chase her!

370
00:32:20,980 --> 00:32:22,730
- Stop running!
- Stop running!

371
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,160
Stop running!

372
00:32:58,210 --> 00:33:01,460
Was everything okay at the press conference?

373
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:03,300
All the major news outlets came.

374
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:05,550
You were headline news for all of them.

375
00:33:43,090 --> 00:33:46,450
♫ My last wish is to never regret ♫

376
00:33:46,450 --> 00:33:52,520
♫ Brave out the heartbreak to no longer be afraid of heartbreaks ♫

377
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:58,830
♫ I choose to bid farewell with a smile ♫

378
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:03,030
Was everything okay at the press conference?

379
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:04,980
All the major news outlets came.

380
00:34:04,980 --> 00:34:07,060
You were headline news for all of them.

381
00:34:59,860 --> 00:35:01,960
- Throw her out.
- Okay.

382
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,020
Hey! Hey!

383
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:04,230
Get up!

384
00:35:04,230 --> 00:35:07,000
What are you doing? Let me go!

385
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:07,980
Get out!

386
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,970
Let me go!

387
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,810
What happened outside?

388
00:35:16,810 --> 00:35:18,930
Nothing. We just met a crazy person.

389
00:35:18,930 --> 00:35:20,970
It's all taken care of now.

390
00:35:25,170 --> 00:35:27,120
What were we discussing earlier?

391
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,710
What should our next steps be?

392
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:30,900
The reporters were asking that today.

393
00:35:37,170 --> 00:35:40,610
Young Master Tianxing, I know you and Miss are not on good terms,

394
00:35:40,610 --> 00:35:43,260
but I beg you, please save Miss.

395
00:35:43,260 --> 00:35:45,630
Now, you are the only person who can save her.

396
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:47,170
Please.

397
00:35:52,120 --> 00:35:55,040
[Qinghai Hospital]

398
00:36:18,130 --> 00:36:20,750
Let me go!

399
00:36:20,750 --> 00:36:23,680
I’m sorry, this is my friend. She went to the wrong hospital.

400
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:26,340
Take care of your friend. This is causing us trouble.

401
00:36:26,340 --> 00:36:28,330
Okay, okay. No problems.

402
00:36:28,330 --> 00:36:30,170
I'm sorry.

403
00:36:30,870 --> 00:36:32,720
Let's go.

404
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:38,460
[Green Mountain Psychiatric Sanatorium]

405
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:04,320
What must I do to meet He Tianxing?

406
00:37:08,270 --> 00:37:10,460
He Mingli used to be the chairwoman,

407
00:37:10,460 --> 00:37:14,170
but she went crazy and was sent to a mental hospital.

408
00:37:14,170 --> 00:37:17,700
He Tianxing is at Green Mountain Psychiatric Sanatorium.

409
00:37:17,700 --> 00:37:22,070
So now Tianliang Group's chairman

410
00:37:23,870 --> 00:37:30,030
is He Tianjian.

411
00:37:32,040 --> 00:37:33,870
[Tianliang Group Chairman]
[He Tianjian]

412
00:37:33,870 --> 00:37:35,880
He Tianjian?

413
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:38,360
He's a hottie, too.

414
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:41,430
He family really has godly genetics.

415
00:37:41,430 --> 00:37:44,310
You aren't going to tell me

416
00:37:44,310 --> 00:37:48,440
that he's He Tianxing's half-brother, with the same dad, are you?

417
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:50,560
How did you know?

418
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:02,540
[Power changes hands twice in one year! He Tianjian will take over as the new chairman.]

419
00:38:10,290 --> 00:38:12,760
I'm his brother.

420
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:18,600
He Tianjian! Remove the source of our troubles!

421
00:38:18,600 --> 00:38:21,400
Did you forget what we did to his mother?

422
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,920
I'm fine.

423
00:38:29,060 --> 00:38:32,590
Sure enough, it’s you. No matter where I go, it’s you.

424
00:38:37,240 --> 00:38:40,860
There's something I should have done earlier.

425
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:44,000
It's just that I didn't have the courage before.

426
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,370
What do you mean?

427
00:38:49,270 --> 00:38:51,090
Nothing. It's just something small.

428
00:38:51,090 --> 00:38:52,880
I can take care of it myself.

429
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:54,970
Are you sure?

430
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:09,610
[Jiankang Police Station]

431
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:29,040
I want to report a case.

432
00:39:29,780 --> 00:39:32,090
Miss, what case do you want to report?

433
00:39:32,090 --> 00:39:37,750
It was not an accident that Tianliang Group's former CEO, He Tianxing, fell from the building.

434
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:40,030
Someone pushed him down.

435
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:41,970
[CID Agent]

436
00:39:41,970 --> 00:39:46,190
I’m sure. The person who pushed the former CEO of Tianliang Group, He Tianxing, off the building

437
00:39:46,190 --> 00:39:49,500
is the current chairman, He Tianjian.

438
00:39:49,500 --> 00:39:53,050
You must really be sure. You can’t simply say things like this.

439
00:39:53,050 --> 00:39:56,900
I’m sure. I saw it using a drone. The image was very clear.

440
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:59,640
Then did you record it?

441
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:03,550
I saw it through my mobile phone. I didn’t record it.

442
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,430
Then you don’t have any evidence.

443
00:40:05,430 --> 00:40:07,910
I saw it with my own eyes.

444
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:12,380
If that's the case, then why are you only coming now to report the case?

445
00:40:13,170 --> 00:40:15,350
It’s because I was sick before.

446
00:40:15,350 --> 00:40:18,020
I was unconscious in the hospital for three months.

447
00:40:19,710 --> 00:40:21,780
Miss Zheng, let me remind you.

448
00:40:21,780 --> 00:40:24,250
Using a drone to spy on another person’s private matters

449
00:40:24,250 --> 00:40:27,600
is already a violation of privacy laws.

450
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:29,020
This is illegal.

451
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:32,020
You can be sentenced for this. Do you know that?

452
00:40:36,050 --> 00:40:39,610
I know all that, but I must do this.

453
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,820
How is that possible? How could Tianxing wake up?

454
00:40:43,820 --> 00:40:47,020
How is that possible? It shouldn't be like this.

455
00:40:47,020 --> 00:40:49,070
It's okay. Don't worry.

456
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:54,680
Don't forget that you're the chairman that the board elected officially.

457
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:56,750
But on the will, it says—

458
00:40:56,750 --> 00:40:58,050
The will is the will.

459
00:40:58,050 --> 00:40:59,430
After the old chairman died,

460
00:40:59,430 --> 00:41:01,790
all of the board members were on your side.

461
00:41:01,790 --> 00:41:03,130
Even though Tianxing woke up,

462
00:41:03,130 --> 00:41:05,420
what use is it if he can't get the support of the board?

463
00:41:05,420 --> 00:41:07,750
The situation is more powerful than the person.

464
00:41:07,750 --> 00:41:10,970
He Tianxing has already lost his best opportunity.

465
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:16,250
Uncle Hu, thank goodness you're supporting me.

466
00:41:20,410 --> 00:41:22,760
You won't suddenly change sides, right?

467
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:24,490
You don't even trust me?

468
00:41:24,490 --> 00:41:26,780
If I don't support you, who am I going to support?

469
00:41:27,710 --> 00:41:29,580
That's true.

470
00:41:32,010 --> 00:41:33,960
Let me take this call.

471
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:37,960
Hello?

472
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:47,340
Someone reported that the chairman is a suspect in causing He Tianxing to fall from the building?

473
00:41:55,770 --> 00:41:58,070
Is what the police said true?

474
00:41:59,170 --> 00:42:01,530
Uncle Hu, that was an accident. I really didn't do it on purpose—

475
00:42:01,530 --> 00:42:04,430
When something this big happened, why didn't you tell me?

476
00:42:10,230 --> 00:42:12,340
It was Tianjian?

477
00:42:12,340 --> 00:42:14,100
Tianliang Group's He Tianjian?

478
00:42:14,100 --> 00:42:17,590
Someone used a drone and saw first hand the course of events that led to your fall.

479
00:42:17,590 --> 00:42:20,560
Moreover, she clearly pointed out that the one who pushed you

480
00:42:20,560 --> 00:42:24,100
was Tianliang Group's current chairman, He Tianjian.

481
00:42:24,100 --> 00:42:26,070
He seemed like such a good person,

482
00:42:26,070 --> 00:42:27,840
but it turned out that he's even crueler than his sister.

483
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:31,360
I find it hard to believe that it's really him.

484
00:42:38,550 --> 00:42:43,000
On the day of the board meeting, we did in fact find a drone.

485
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:45,330
Where is the drone?

486
00:42:45,330 --> 00:42:47,430
It's been taken care of.

487
00:42:49,380 --> 00:42:52,570
Right now, where is the person who violated privacy laws?

488
00:42:52,570 --> 00:42:57,000
The case is still being investigated, so we let her go home for now.

489
00:42:58,190 --> 00:43:01,840
If she really saw the truth of me falling off the building,

490
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:05,370
her safety will be compromised.

491
00:43:05,370 --> 00:43:07,210
[CEO, You're So Naughty]

492
00:43:07,210 --> 00:43:10,390
I told you that the counterattack of the female antagonist wasn't a worthwhile plot.

493
00:43:10,390 --> 00:43:11,930
Who wants to read that?

494
00:43:11,930 --> 00:43:14,800
Just great. The negative reviews are everywhere now.

495
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:16,540
Why are you so stubborn?

496
00:43:16,540 --> 00:43:18,330
Why didn't you listen?

497
00:43:18,330 --> 00:43:21,330
I did listen, and I asked the author to change it,

498
00:43:21,330 --> 00:43:25,030
but I don't know how it got worse after it was fixed.

499
00:43:25,030 --> 00:43:26,880
When it was published, it was still like this.

500
00:43:26,880 --> 00:43:28,830
I don't want to hear this.

501
00:43:28,830 --> 00:43:31,280
They're all excuses, justifications!

502
00:43:31,280 --> 00:43:33,400
No excuse!

503
00:43:34,940 --> 00:43:39,280
I'm sorry. I also don't know why this happened.

504
00:43:39,280 --> 00:43:42,330
Sorry? Is sorry any use?

505
00:43:42,330 --> 00:43:43,940
Apologies are all fake!

506
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:46,360
Only money is real.

507
00:43:47,380 --> 00:43:49,680
What is wrong with this year?

508
00:43:49,680 --> 00:43:52,270
Not a single good thing happened.

509
00:43:52,270 --> 00:43:54,710
There is! There is a good thing. Xiao'en finally woke up.

510
00:43:54,710 --> 00:43:56,680
She was already discharged from the hospital.

511
00:43:56,680 --> 00:43:58,360
Really?

512
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:02,100
What is wrong with my jaw?

513
00:44:02,100 --> 00:44:04,540
